{"tid":847440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人最感恩既事情就係生長係一個反政府既家庭，而唔係藍絲家庭？","createTime":"2018-10-04T07:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T14:54:32.000Z","uid":20032,"like":18,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"473f15cf821aa0fe911da4ca46bef0acb47a3546","tid":847440,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"諗翻起佔中既時期，好多屋企，好多朋友既屋企都鬧得好僵<br />\n<br />\n而我係佢地之中最輕鬆既一個，因為我父母都ban左，唔比再返大陸，逼住留係香港<br />\n<br />\n但佢地好睇唔過眼香港既法例，原因係兩老都好鍾意食狗肉，準確d黎講係成家都鍾意，但我同阿哥有得返大陸，所以對依方面無乜怨氣，兩老就覺得香港無得食狗肉好on9<br />\n<br />\n所以佢認為我參加佔中係一件好事，因為係佢地眼中香港政府係衰人<br />\n<br />\n我就算無感受過親人既阻止，但都好明白同屋企鬧翻既感覺，唔好受，孤軍作戰<br />\n<br />\n但其實連登有好多巴打都係同路人，唔好放棄！"},{"pid":"40796401f97a88f60516ee40ecde771a2ec79d2c","tid":847440,"uid":190889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"唉我都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係夜晚去日頭返屋企訓<br />\n但返屋企既時候都係要同佢地嘈<br />\n感覺好似無地方休息咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722eb739d8db4fd2dee760d6f713126ddbffd36c","tid":847440,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"狗肉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e48e495c957adf71d125a0ef71408288f95df64","tid":847440,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722eb739d8db4fd2dee760d6f713126ddbffd36c","tid":847440,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"狗肉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"後話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n標題係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc8f8fe46c8140d69931e04f140076702f32e4c","tid":847440,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40796401f97a88f60516ee40ecde771a2ec79d2c"